{"word":"ἐρυμνῶδις","slug":"ἐρυμνῶδις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n42793\" key=\"e)rumnw=dis\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐρυμνῶδις</orth> (sic)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">· λύπην καὶ φλεγμονὴν παρέχων, ἢ ὑπερήφανον,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> (cf. Lat. <sense id=\"n42793.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">aerumnosus</tr_>). <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ἐρυμός·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ζεύς, καὶ ζυγός, καὶ ζεύγλη,</foreign> Id. (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥυμός</foreign>). <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐρύμυλον·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸν μεγάλως μυκώμενον ταῦρον</foreign> (leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρύγμηλον</foreign>), Id. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐρυνόν·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σκοτεινόν, ἠσφαλισμένον,</foreign> Id. (confusion of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρεμνόν</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρυμνόν</foreign>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}